                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="cafe.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Green Pizza</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Assorted Organic Heirloom Tomatoes, Red Onions, Mozzarella, French Goat Cheese, 
                            Fresh Herbs, and Garlic Olive Oil.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

